Through intimate conversations with her family and team, we get to know Ana’s motivations, the obstacles she has faced and the dreams she keeps chasing. Her career, from its origins in a small town in Murcia to being the first woman to win the World Championship, is a source of inspiration for anyone. Ana herself is a clear example of overcoming struggle and tenacity, and her story which is full of exciting moments encourages us all to fight for our dreams.

programme.title: Eighteam
programme.desc: The Chipolopolo is the Zambia national team that at the 1988 Olympic thrashes Italy 4-0 and has their eyes on the Africa Cup of Nations. But in 1993 a Zambian Air Force ditches into the ocean about 500 metres offshore from Gabon. All passengers, including 18 players, die in the accident.The Chipolopolo's captain, Kalusha Bwalya, who is not aboard the ill-fated flight puts his efforts to build a new team and make a professional federation becoming later the national team coach and president of the Football Association of Zambia. Two decades later, destiny makes Zambia a blink: in Gabon, Zambia becomes African champions for the first time after a long penalty shoot-out. There are 18 penalties.

programme.title: Made in Senegal

programme.title: Everyday Spartans: Episode 1
programme.desc: Joe De Sena – Spartan Founder and Team Leader welcomes the team to Japan where they must climb iconic Mt. Fuji. As their first challenge, they scale the Atago stairs, a Samurai-honored tradition with a kettlebell for company. If that’s not enough, De Sena makes them run around the famed Imperial Palace. However, this time around there is a surprise for them from Rakuten. What other surprises are around the corner?

programme.title: Everyday Spartans: Episode 2
programme.desc: The Spartans are all set to climb Mt.Fuji a challenge that not only requires physical prowess but tremendous mental strength. A Japanese monk helps the Spartans cleanse their minds by guiding them through the time-tested practice of taking on the full force of an icy-cold waterfall – an experience they will never forget. As they undertake their arduous climb, their egos and frayed nerves begin to get in the way of staying together as a team. The shared responsibility of lugging along a 45-kg accessory certainly does not help their cause. Will they come together before it’s too late?

programme.title: Everyday Spartans: Episode 3
programme.desc: While the team begins to come together as one, awareness dawns on how different their individual attitudes and confidence levels are. While one of them, realizes they cannot complete the task and prepares to descend, another questions if her pace is setting everyone back. Keeping her on and walking at her pace would mean sacrificing watching the prized sunrise at the summit. Are they ready to give up on that ? They are getting beaten down, but they must go on. Will they make it before sunrise?

programme.title: Everyday Spartans: Episode 4
programme.desc: A sea of clouds and a magical sunrise await the team at the summit. With the team’s belief in themselves and each other reinforced, they think about what it took to overcome their obstacles. The moment is especially poignant for one member who pays tribute to the memory of his late son and spends a quiet moment in remembrance of him. As each of them grapple with the emotions that overtake them on the summit, Joe De Sena reminds them that reaching the summit is not the end of their journey – its’s only the beginning. Where will the Spartan spirit take them next?

programme.title: Everyday Spartans: Episode 5
programme.desc: After an extraordinary adventure in Japan, the Spartans head to America . De Sena is not pleased with the baggage they are carrying– lateness, injuries and poor body maintenance. Will an extended dip in an icy lake shake their reverie? Under the guidance of a survival expert, they must climb a massive rock as one unit with only a rope holding them all together. Every member must think every step through for the sake of the team. For, one miscalculated step could very well lead to disaster. Can they handle the heat of this challenge?

programme.title: The Secrets of La Roja – World Champions 2010

Despite this successful ending, “La Roja” had to overcome various struggles and difficulties in order to become legendary. The team arrived in South Africa with the triumph of the 2008 European Football Championship under their belt and Vicente del Bosque leading the way. There was a general feeling of favoritism attributed to ""La Roja"" and while the defeat against Switzerland in the first match came as a shock, it motivated Del Bosque and his team to come together and focus on one intention: good football and one goal: to make history.

Amid this family struggle we see Jesus wrestling not only with Satan, but also with his own faith.

Frightened and unsure of himself to begin with, he soon becomes more skilled in his new line of work, targeting those he believes deserve it most. However a close friend, who is a cop, begins to suspect that there may be more to Bill than first appears.

programme.title: Guardians of the Tomb

In their quest to rescue him, they find themselves underground, battling ancient, terrifying Chinese magic and making their way through a swarm of deadly, man-eating spiders – only to uncover the secret behind the insects’ power and intelligence.

But when he's assigned to escort a petty criminal to testify before the grand jury, a violent turn of events means this down-and-out cop needs to pull it together to save not only the life of the witness but his own as they are hunted across the city. The clock is ticking in this exhilarating race against time. Will justice be served or will there be two more bodies to add to the crime toll of the city?

However, his joy is short-lived, as, on the very same day, the people of Earth become plagued with terrifying visions of the end of the world. When a gigantic, all-consuming alien mothership appears in the sky and launches a ruthless attack on Earth's cities, chaos and destruction follow. Tom must find the strength and wisdom to save his wife and unborn child. However, first he must confront a shocking truth. A truth which threatens the key to the survival of the human race. The ultimate war for Planet Earth is about to begin...

With the fate of his world, and his family at stake, Mariah will risk everything to unravel the Curse of the Midas Box!
